Plot: A group of friends, just looking to have a good time in a rave party on a remote island in Goa, find out that the island is infested with Zombies.
Title: Go Goa Gone
Writer: Krishna D.K. (story and screenplay), Kunal Khemu (dialogue), Sita Menon (dialogue), Sita Menon (story and screenplay), Raj Nidimoru (story and screenplay), Raja Sen (additional dialogue)
Actors: Saif Ali Khan, Kunal Khemu, Vir Das, Anand Tiwari
